	quests: [
		{
			description: [
				"&eCobblemon Unchained&r removes the restrictions that make certain Cobblemon mechanics impossible to access in single-player — primarily trade evolutions and other multiplayer-dependent features."
				""
				"In standard Cobblemon, Cobblemon like Machamp, Alakazam, and Gengar require trading to evolve. On a solo server or small group, that can lock entire evolution lines permanently."
				""
				"Unchained fixes that. Check its config to see which restrictions have been lifted in this pack."
				""
				"&7Tip: Unchained may remove trade-evolution restrictions — check its config for enabled features.&r"
			]
			icon: "cobblemon:link_cable"
			id: "10000000000000B5"
			min_width: 340
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "10000000000000B4"
				item: "cobblemon:rare_candy"
				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "Cobblemon Unchained"
			tasks: [{
				id: "10000000000000B3"
				title: "Use a Cobblemon Unchained feature"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "&bFreed from the Box"
			x: 0.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["10000000000000B5"]
			description: [
				"The &eLink Cable&r replaces the trade mechanic for solo play. Craft one and use it on a Cobblemon that normally requires trading to evolve — it triggers the evolution immediately."
				""
				"This unlocks some of the strongest fully-evolved Cobblemon in the game. Machamp, Alakazam, Gengar, Golem, Slowbro via King's Rock — all now accessible without a second player."
				""
				"Craft your first Link Cable and have it ready. You probably already have a Cobblemon waiting for it."
				""
				"&7Tip: Trade evolution lines like Machamp and Alakazam are now fully accessible solo.&r"
			]
			id: "10000000000000B8"
			min_width: 340
			rewards: [{
				id: "10000000000000B7"
				item: "cobblemon:link_cable"
				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "No Trader Needed"
			tasks: [{
				consume_items: false
				id: "10000000000000B6"
				item: "cobblemon:link_cable"
				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "&bLink Cable Crafter"
			x: 2.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["10000000000000B8"]
			description: [
				"Three different trade-evolution Cobblemon evolved using Unchained mechanics. This means three Link Cable uses, three evolution lines completed, and three Cobblemon that were previously inaccessible now on your team."
				""
				"Plan your team around these unlocked lines. Some of them are among the best Cobblemon available, and they were just locked away until now."
				""
				"Unchained turns solo play into full play. Use everything it gives you."
				""
				"&7Tip: Plan your team around full evolution lines — they're now all available to you.&r"
			]
			id: "10000000000000BB"
			min_width: 330
			rewards: [{
				count: 3
				id: "10000000000000BA"
				item: "cobblemon:pp_max"
				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "hexagon"
			subtitle: "Self-Sufficient Trainer"
			tasks: [{
