		{
			dependencies: ["10000000000000BE"]
			description: [
				"Cobblemon spawn tables have been extended to include biomes added by mods in this pack. Terralith, Blue Skies, The Aether, and other dimension mods all contribute new habitats with unique Cobblemon populations."
				""
				"Species you can't find in vanilla biomes may appear exclusively in modded ones. If you've been ignoring the modded dimensions — &eThe Aether&r in particular — now is the time to explore them."
				""
				"The Aether's floating islands are home to Cobblemon you simply won't encounter anywhere else. Go there."
				""
				"&7Tip: Many Cobblemon have modded biome spawn entries — explore new dimensions for unique species.&r"
			]
