		{
			dependencies: ["10000000000000C1"]
			description: [
				"Cobblemon Integrations enables your team to participate in combat scenarios from other mods — Gateways to Eternity waves, Twilight Forest boss encounters, and similar high-stakes events."
				""
				"These fights are harder than standard wild battles. They're designed for geared Minecraft players, and your Cobblemon team has to keep up."
				""
				"Put your strongest, most levelled Cobblemon at the front and trust your training. This is what all those battles were building toward."
				""
				"&7Tip: Some integrations allow Cobblemon to assist in gateway and dungeon encounters.&r"
			]
